summary: My take on a Ganondorf preset for Racemenu
descriptionHtml:
while sitting around and waiting for some requests for presets i decided that it would be a good idea to create Ganondorf. there are 2 versions both labeled in the pictures to its corresponding download

Required
Beards - [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/28363/?]http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/28363/?[/url]
Brows - [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/30411/?]http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/30411/?[/url]
Apachii Sky Hair - [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/10168/?]http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/10168/?[/url]
Eyes of Aber - [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/59192/?]http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/59192/?[/url]
Superior Lore-Friendly Hair - [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/36510/?]http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/36510/?[/url]
WSCO - Windsong Skyrim Character Overhaul - [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/52322/?]http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/52322/?[/url]

Recomended
Relics of Hyrule (for the armor and weapons used in the screenshots) - [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/40615/?]http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/40615/?[/url]
